As javadoc suggests, you should add following line to avoid interaction with other tests. It can also detect that some threads cannot finish:
assertTrue("Deadlock detected!", executor.awaitTermination(10, TimeUnit.SECONDS));
EDIT: I updated this several times, I was sleepy yesterday and could not decide between assertTrue/assertFalse, sorry :D

